description.author: Hamish Mackenzie
description.synopsis: DOM library that supports both GHCJS and WebKitGTK
description.description:
Documentent Object Model (DOM) functions that work with
GHCJS, but can also be used with GHC and WebKitGTK.

package-flags.name: old-webkit
package-flags.description:
If you have an old version of WebKitGTK+ this will get ghcjs-dom
to build, leaving out functions that are new or have changed.
This option is mainly here to get the travis builds to work.

package-flags.name: gtk3
package-flags.description: Use GTK3 rather than GTK2 (only matters when using webkit)
